chefs.bio: Chef Chen Wei is a culinary prodigy whose passion has taken him around the world. Experienced in French, Italian, and Asian cuisine, he has earned repute in the kitchen as well as recognition among the food critics.
chefs.ingredients: Chicken, Parmesan cheese, Marinara sauce, Mozzarella cheese, Bread crumbs, Olive oil
chefs.cookingMethod:
1. Preheat the oven to 375. 
2. Coat the chicken in bread crumbs and fry until golden brown.
